Package org.apache.storm.trident.windowing

Interface WindowsStore

All Superinterfaces:
Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
InMemoryWindowsStore
public interface WindowsStore extends Serializable
Store for storing window related entities like windowed tuples, triggers etc. WindowKryoSerializer can be used for kryo serialization/deserialization of keys and values.
